title: New Scientist Magazine. 6 November 2010.
description:
New Scientist Magazine. 6 November 2010.

New Scientist is a weekly international science magazine 
and website covering recent developments in science and 
technology for a general English-speaking audience. New 
Scientist has maintained a website since 1996, publishing 
daily news. As well as covering current events and news 
from the scientific community, the magazine often features 
speculative articles, ranging from the technical to the 
philosophical.

Enjoy.
